title: #92Noon! Sickman, Guys in The Cornfield, Jonny Athletic, Feast
description: Friday Football Feast. The Wild's Media Relations Director Aaron Sickman calls in to talk the upcoming season and Wild On The Water fishing tournament. The guys in the cornfield stop by to talk horse racing, the US Open and being a Dad. A 90 second phone call with Mike Zimmer on his race horse, Gina Baby. The controversy and tragedy at Santa Anita Track is an isolated incident and not the norm. And fellow basketball snob, Jonny Athletic, talks the NBA and getting to watch the final game with Gersson Rosas.
